    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the mince is caramelising, add your <strong>tortillas</strong> to a plate</p><p>Put the plate in the <strong>microwave</strong> and cook for 20 secs on high or until the tortillas are warmed through</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1581514829336-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
