            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>peanut butter</strong>, <strong>chilli relish</strong>,<strong> remaining soy sauce</strong>,<strong> </strong>the juice of your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, a splash of <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>satay sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1620224267222-x200.jpg",
